  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Total Knee Arthroplasty (TKA) is a common orthopedic surgery usually leads to Bleeding. The
      null hypothesis of this study was that TA has no effect on post surgical bleeding in patients
      undergoes TKA.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
